vmwVRNIAgentCapabilityMIB.description: This module defines agent capabilities for deployed VRNI agents by release.

vmwVRNIAgent2017v330.name: vmwVRNIAgent2017v330
vmwVRNIAgent2017v330.description: Release 3.3.0 for VMware VRNI supporting only SNMPv2c trap PDUs. It describes all the notifications sent from the VRNI appliance. This mib module is backward compatible with next version. It extends 3.2 release events by appending eventName managed object to each notification's variable binding and adding a new set of notifications.
